title: Athletics at the 2015 Southeast Asian Games – Women's 10,000 metres
text: The women's 10,000 metres at the <a href="2015%20Southeast%20Asian%20Games">2015 Southeast Asian Games</a> was held in <a href="National%20Stadium%2C%20Singapore">National Stadium</a>, <a href="Singapore">Singapore</a>. The <a href="track%20and%20field">track and field</a> events took place on June 11.
